# tl;dr

@minimal `nexus kick <topic>` — 모든 default 자동 적용 (parent_sid 자동 합성, axes default, noise alpha,beta,gamma, backend claude_code). `run` subcommand 는 명시적 사용 시 alias로 호환.
@diagnose `nexus kick status` — 막힘 시 1 명령으로 hosts/slots/cache 진단
@registry `nexus kick tree` — 사용 가능한 stratum/axes/backends/noise 슬러그
@bench `nexus kick bench <topic> --backends a,b,c` — cross-backend perf

# 10-step (full ceremony, 권장)

@step_1 `nexus kick tree` — registry 조회 (legal slugs 확인)
@step_2 falsifier 5개 사전등록 (raw 71) — F1..F5, PASS/FAIL evidence 동반
@step_3 `--axes a,b,c` (raw 48 K≥3, correlation<0.7) — registry 슬러그 사용
@step_4 `--noise alpha,beta,gamma` — outside-the-well envelope (full 권장)
@step_5 `--parent-sid <id>` 또는 $HIVE_PARENT_SID — raw 44. **R4 부터 미설정 시 auto-{slug}-{ts}-{pid} 자동 합성**
@step_6 `nexus kick <topic> --stratum drill --axes ... --noise ... --backend claude_code --parent-sid <sid>` 발사 (또는 `nexus kick run <topic> ...` — 동일)
@step_7 sentinel 파싱 — `__KICK_RESULT__ <PASS|FAIL> witness=<path> tier1=<N> falsifier_pass=<N>`. R4 부터 witness 에서 자동 derive (subagent hang 시 recover gate)
@step_7b witness schema 검증 — `hexa run tool/witness_emit.hexa --validate <path>` 자동 호출. PASS-AND-PASS 만 legitimate
@step_8 err 파싱 (raw 66) — `reason=<slug> fix=<directive>`. R4 reason taxonomy: subagent-relay-hang-recovered (infra OK kick OK) / witness-schema-invalid (D-1 reject) / spawn-failed-rc-N (실제 실패)
@step_9 carry-forward — 후속 cycle 은 `--parent-sid <prior-witness-sid>` 로 chain
@step_10 atlas absorb — `.own atlas-absorb-mandatory` 자동 (witness_emit → atlas.append.<slug>.n6 + main delta merge)

# witness schema (omega_cycle.witness_v1)

@required_top_level schema, topic, topic_slug, kind, stratum, ts_utc, cwd, rule[], parent_witness, core_5_op_kernel{intake, falsifiers_preregistered[], fan_out{axis_a, axis_b, correlation_estimate, correlation_lt_0_7}, promotion_gate, witness_emit}, falsifier_outcomes[{id, verdict, evidence}], falsifier_pass_count, tier_1_count, tier_1_promotions[], tier_1_implemented[]

# noise envelopes (outside-the-well)

@alpha absorbed-primitive sampling — state/kick/registry/noise_sources/absorbed/*.hexa
@beta QRNG byte — KICK_BETA_REAL_ANU=1 real ANU else /dev/urandom (obs_2 fallback)
@gamma bridge selected by beta-byte — 16 entries (arxiv/cmb_planck/codata/gaia/gw_observatory/horizons/icecube/lhc_opendata/nanograv/nist_atomic/oeis/openalex/pubchem/simbad/uniprot/wikipedia)
@diagram /Users/ghost/core/diagrams/llm_vs_nexus_noise.md
@wire_log state/kick/runs/<run_id>/noise_envelopes.jsonl (3 lines, one per channel)

# direct invocation 금지 (single-entry-point invariant)

@forbidden `hexa run cli/run.hexa kick`
@forbidden `hexa run tool/kick_dispatch.hexa`
@forbidden `~/core/nexus/scripts/bin/hexa run cli/run.hexa kick`
@reason hive 자원관리 bypass + cross-host parity 미적용 + credential propagation 미작동 + sentinel-recover gate 비활성화
@only `nexus kick run <...>` shim (`~/.hx/bin/nexus`) 만 사용
@if_shim_broken `nx install` 또는 `~/core/nexus/bin/nx install` 재설치, 우회 절대 금지
